{"tid":2359491,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"碩士生體現心靈富足便豪華 劏房補習社　水桶上教學","createTime":"2021-01-09T03:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T04:54:52.000Z","uid":248054,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de056965d4b5ae4dc5cf628852f6aed0ae62de1a","tid":2359491,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:09:48.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「君子居無求安」，屈居40呎劏房一樣住得「豪華」。29歲中大碩士林小龍，去年因家庭問題被迫入住元朗40呎劏房。生於小康之家的資優生，突變獨居隱青；劏房戶的人和事，他不習慣；為交學費及租金，他在40呎劏房內為8名中學生補習，自己蹲在廁所講書。今年他把劏房奇遇出版成書《我的豪華劏房生活》，盼勉勵同路人「心靈富足就豪華」。"},{"pid":"64666db7dc9acdad71c99f413628d580e21006f2","tid":2359491,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tBhjlSirxY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-tBhjlSirxY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=77dbf7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tBhjlSirxY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"98f632a29f32c57ce2f8b6ffc3345f0ab2dc8e3b","tid":2359491,"uid":248054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"中大碩士生嘅心態好積極<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3d6e5b745c38c07d0a55174071b2623b37ad22","tid":2359491,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"問君能有幾多愁，恰似一群太監上青樓"},{"pid":"4a0bce74619d3919be0c6094ce237c95f2bd49f3","tid":2359491,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3d6e5b745c38c07d0a55174071b2623b37ad22","tid":2359491,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"問君能有幾多愁，恰似一群太監上青樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"最緊要積極面對人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h